snippet.title: Tonic Trouble Trailer 1999
snippet.description:
Tonic Trouble Trailer 1999

Official Content From UbiSoft

You are Ed, a friendly extraterrestrial retrieving a mysterious can you accidentally dumped on Earth. The can's contents have turned the entire planet upside down. Your mission fix the mishap and stop Grogh from using the can's contents to dominate the world. You'll solve zany problems, avoid enemy traps and attacks throughout outrageous worlds.
Platforms: Nintendo 64, PC CD

Nintendo 64, PC CD
